# transcode: add VAAPI, libvorbis and libopus default codec and stream profiles
#
# The default webtv codec and stream profiles only included software encoders
# (libvpx, libx264, vorbis, aac). This patch adds hardware-accelerated VAAPI
# and QSV variants and modern audio codecs as defaults:
#
# New codec profiles:
#   webtv-vp8-vaapi    - VP8  hardware encoder via VAAPI (rc_mode=VBR, 1500kbps)
#   webtv-h264-qsv     - H264 hardware encoder via QSV   (rc_mode=auto, 1500kbps)
#   webtv-h264-vaapi   - H264 hardware encoder via VAAPI (rc_mode=auto, 1500kbps)
#   webtv-hevc-qsv     - HEVC hardware encoder via QSV   (rc_mode=auto, 1500kbps)
#   webtv-hevc-vaapi   - HEVC hardware encoder via VAAPI (rc_mode=auto, 1500kbps)
#   webtv-libvorbis    - libvorbis encoder, stereo default (channel_layout=3)
#   webtv-libopus      - libopus encoder, stereo/128kbps/constrained-VBR default
#
# Updated codec profiles:
#   webtv-aac          - added channel_layout=3 (stereo) and sample_rate=48000
#
# New stream hwaccel profiles (with software equivalent):
#   webtv-vp8-vaapi-opus-webm      - VP8 VAAPI + libopus, WEBM
#   webtv-vp9-vaapi-opus-webm      - VP9 VAAPI + libopus, WEBM
#   webtv-h264-qsv-aac-matroska    - H264 VAAPI + AAC, Matroska
#   webtv-h264-qsv-aac-mp4         - H264 VAAPI + AAC, MP4
#   webtv-h264-vaapi-aac-matroska  - H264 VAAPI + AAC, Matroska
#   webtv-h264-vaapi-aac-mp4       - H264 VAAPI + AAC, MP4
#   webtv-hevc-qsv-aac-matroska    - HEVC VAAPI + AAC, Matroska
#   webtv-hevc-qsv-aac-mp4         - HEVC VAAPI + AAC, MP4
#   webtv-hevc-vaapi-aac-matroska  - HEVC VAAPI + AAC, Matroska
#   webtv-hevc-vaapi-aac-mp4       - HEVC VAAPI + AAC, MP4
#
# Software fallback profiles are preserved for systems without VAAPI support.
# Stereo (channel_layout=3) is set as default for all audio codecs to ensure
# correct downmix from multichannel sources (e.g. AC3 5.1) without requiring
# manual configuration.
#
--- data/conf/transcoder/codecs.orig	2026-05-19 20:37:17.000000000 +0000
